00:43:11,481 --> 00:43:12,225
Scott: And then that would in.

627
00:43:12,266 --> 00:43:14,899
Scott: so you would get software and install it on its own.

628
00:43:15,561 --> 00:43:23,120
Scott: And all these different softwares that were coming from different places would be installed alongside each other on the same computer.

629
00:43:23,641 --> 00:43:25,870
Scott: Sometimes cause problems, sometimes not.

630
00:43:25,931 --> 00:43:28,080
Scott: There are ways to make it work, right?

631
00:43:28,360 --> 00:43:32,517
