00:45:23,066 --> 00:45:23,188
Rym: Yeah.

657
00:45:25,540 --> 00:45:26,522
Scott: Pac-Man, I don't know.

658
00:45:27,244 --> 00:45:34,840
Scott: And there's a piece of software that is like the package manager that connects to a repository somewhere where all the software is.

