00:46:14,981 --> 00:46:15,161
Scott: Right.

677
00:46:15,201 --> 00:46:22,620
Scott: Because some software is just, you know, for interpreted languages like, you know, Python or Perl and or Ruby.

678
00:46:23,764 --> 00:46:24,988
Scott: And it's not compiled.

