00:50:02,480 --> 00:50:05,653
Scott: One of them uses library version three and one of them uses four.

740
00:50:06,014 --> 00:50:07,339
Scott: What the hell do I do about that?

741
00:50:07,380 --> 00:50:07,480
Scott: Right.

742
00:50:08,000 --> 00:50:09,350
Scott: What the hell do I do about that?

743
00:50:09,370 --> 00:50:09,994
Scott: Right.

744
00:50:10,055 --> 00:50:10,739
Scott: There's all these issues.

745
00:50:11,200 --> 00:50:19,620
Scott: So what's come to be is that most major programming languages these days, I think Perl was the first major one.

