00:51:11,468 --> 00:51:15,340
Scott: When I install things for project one, don't install them on the global system.

758
00:51:15,981 --> 00:51:19,733
Scott: Use the Python package manager to install libraries in this box.

759
00:51:20,194 --> 00:51:22,140
Scott: You know, virtual environment is what they call it.

760
00:51:22,180 --> 00:51:24,390
Scott: And then I'm working on a different project now.

