00:52:27,896 --> 00:52:28,097
Scott: Right.

786
00:52:28,137 --> 00:52:29,720
Scott: To use it in other projects.

787
00:52:30,380 --> 00:52:33,445
Scott: But you don't want to just share it with the whole frickin world.

