904
01:01:01,260 --> 01:01:01,401
Scott: Yeah.

905
01:01:01,461 --> 01:01:11,911
Scott: You could even write, you know, your program itself that ties together other programs, you could push it out to the repository as yet another program.

906
01:01:12,271 --> 01:01:12,492
Scott: Right.

907
01:01:12,872 --> 01:01:17,016
Scott: And then other people could then install your, you know, install your thing.

908
01:01:17,036 --> 01:01:20,800
