910
01:01:34,580 --> 01:01:39,951
Rym: But even whatever, say you get a dodgy package for like, that's not used by a lot of people.

911
01:01:40,673 --> 01:01:42,857
Rym: And thus doesn't have as many eyes keeping an eye on it.

912
01:01:43,178 --> 01:01:44,140
Rym: And it does something malicious.

